SILENZIOSA Episode 11: La Royauté Oblige

It’s interesting to note that while THE HAMMER OF FREEDOM is the most-liked series on Arktoons, with nearly 11,000 likes, HYPERGAMOUSE is now the most-viewed series and looks as if it will be the first to 100,000 episode views.
